  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"8 2 []\">\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom:-2.25em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:5px;\">\n     <div style=\"padding: 10px;margin-bottom: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 17px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">很多人都没注意到，谷歌悄悄放了一个大招，既不是 Gemini 也不是 nano banana pro，而是一份报告。</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 5 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;vertical-align:bottom;width:614px !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503183761\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=156887aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVZ7JnPtEEqnkicw1JmIUibze4kI4o76tr2zVE3LC8g6wTX3sBXRJLOJP3ick53GT05KzcjvVROmLoJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic\"></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">《2025 AI 投资回报率报告》</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=349b32fb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0YgiaYAAPNShQWaXQmy9fTTaOy4rtxgicurWicogP9iasxpBEMIYFuNpfibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D0\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这份报告调研了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">全球 3446 名企业高管</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（这些企业年营收都不低于 1000 万美元，不是小卡拉米）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过实打实的案例告诉业界，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">到底应该如何在 AI 上花钱，才能获得最大收益。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3b03f97d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0v7LvrAZnTRxLGV5hBFCd93hVYluTOcuviaa4jK3fAeGfP5qG27j1bicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Google 通过报告指出：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">88% 的早期入坑者，都得到了不错的投资回报，而且，生成式 AI/ 大模型的下一个金矿，是智能体。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;核心结论包括以下几点：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4562841530054645\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1098\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503193138\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b9f7b6b6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVWoFDEfB8g9Z1W5CYHdLUTWvuwYvQzpXMbLz0l0UUNkib9oxKS17zzQnKoLlaEQOIN1Q7liaqgoywZw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 32px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6bd51f52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw01hO4tJgH8IhwYHSLn9r9btjCjHr8fiaYGKXF5TrlQkHzw8SQU4JUHTQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D5\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">虽然已经发布 1 个多月了，但这份报告的含金量还在上升，我们对这份报告进行了全文翻译，以下为完整中文报告：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=24cb3e39&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0YgiaYAAPNShQWaXQmy9fTTaOy4rtxgicurWicogP9iasxpBEMIYFuNpfibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D6\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1cbe7905&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0Vpibia6e1X90lVwruFxftbpXjSSfv5QUoOEaiaShD2RCbLRt7a350ILcg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D7\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=efa6a39d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0n4kEwkF45yDwTmQnJCCq3lfmZzNCJsI0gOueibhRx1T7PKvSpEsAOsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D8\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ec163669&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0wWbLCnGh6nffeGPW6rFWT3RMJBWc0alkbFMvibV8VnIpWlR8qRUPFDw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D9\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c020d91a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0v7LvrAZnTRxLGV5hBFCd93hVYluTOcuviaa4jK3fAeGfP5qG27j1bicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D10\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a449acd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0WInP9V3qXqLJiaQRz0tNAIdx4BluicnbJ5wuVxkSWvL4XqereknZiaKfg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D11\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=63dbc60e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0Ijt0MWrN0fkkkibXtqnKzX5F0cXhJT7qb2ia5S7ia15VZka0vHGcIpAZw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D12\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=80c1d5b4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw03NAWWUPONOLVc4BdqbHogLLo862iav991MFRu90fjC3dkzYqCBqYJow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D13\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">智能体分级</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">一级：简单任务</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，主要是输出内容，并不真正接管业务动作，比如聊天机器人、知识库检索、多模态生成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">二级：智能体应用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，AI 开始为了一个业务目标干活，能在限定范围完成多步任务，从对话走向应用，让 AI 能做动作或者推动流程，可以替代具体岗位里的重复步骤。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">三级：多智能体工作流</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，本质上不是一个智能体干所有活，而是多个角色分工协作，形成端到端流程。能覆盖跨部门、跨系统的复杂业务流程，适合长链路场景比如：从线索到成交、从保修到闭环、从需求到交付。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">一级是工具，二级是产品，三级是系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d6549e3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0QMuUJHUcpWwWxticuY8GgkSlWj8obZkHU0oFJUKT2FIKZK9SFWgS48Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D14\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9e20e5aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw014L87BfPPGibUn072czlGabU0VM8DtsZsAAZV8mssVhcrpxwWhfiaujA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D15\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=014c13da&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0BJbQV3DibYichQ0d0JOdYINItrutxDZxlm3gBTeOlPIZ4fgTria8xZn9g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D16\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=44655381&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0dhF1GE5ibXoz90ZPZoGeeCjQ17oBAsrD1zqAOIicbyHGtqPnYSics5lDw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D17\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">AI 智能体的采用率</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">按地区挺意外的，亚太领跑（调查样本不含中国大陆），北美最慢。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">按行业看医疗反而最谨慎，毕竟人命关天的事儿哈哈哈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-indent: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fc69fd63&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0RVvztqMsp1glknGYf6CugWaTAicD6aJk2hHdy0kDH489OrNcWY9GZcg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D18\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">智能体最先落地在哪些场景</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">第一梯队：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">客户服务与体验 49%、营销增长 46%、安全运营与网络安全 46%、技术支持 45%；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这些场景数据和流程最标准化，容易形成可量化收益。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">中间梯队：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">产品创新与设计 43%、生产力与研究 43%、软件开发 40%、财务与会计 38%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><