.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">真正的预算大头在哪儿呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">往往不在模型调用费，而在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">数据治理、系统集成、权限与安全、评测与运维</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，尤其当企业开始部署智能体时更明显。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当然对于国内企业来说，自己搞算力、训调推模型的话，AI Infra 的费用仍然是大头</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5dca4b7a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw088UHLmPSvxTNk5ribQoOiacvR3jhuZqIqrEF7vaS4AUCr6Ikf4OgRwcw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D48\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 32px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb043332&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0ZMhCbHYLILETsmb6AmXP4cjZWleejboBUMwXg2ribM62ZTRPMP1ibQDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D49\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这两页挺有意思的——</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">搞 