ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ffab41e4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0TKxtAOOy7QBdBy7lXGyibpapibk0hpzmD6hjv3wvtRqvJL1e8pAYEJqA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D52\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">三大落地挑战</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①数据隐私和安全②与现有系统集成③成本</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e4807e8e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0gujghnsE272CnO7sryNQJXiarwpT9qibs3yr4uibx5p8Dr00hJZX9FicfA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D53\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 16px 32px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e05579f9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0yY8tojvd6VE6gVY8R9mVqMiagmiaZeGTF1AxWHiawiaLGaNoyibHowFQWcQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D54\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">智能体行动计划七步法</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">①搞定老板：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">得有 C-level 站台，能拍板、能清障。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">②展示价值：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用一个说得通的业务案例去拿预算，别只画饼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">③立好规矩：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">提前写好企业级 AI 规则，数据、合规、版权 /IP 都要管住。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">④挑准场景：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">优先做那些重复、标准、能省人省时间的流程，ROI 最快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">⑤筑起信任：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">数据治理+安全框架从第一天就上，同时保留人工兜底。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">⑥接入系统：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">智能体要能干活，就得接入内部业务系统，但权限要可控可审计。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">⑦投技术更要投人：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">培训内训、培养人才。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=31658ac0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FpEeuqRbicF543W0WUZXTtB20ib7QOAfFw0g5elHnTvB3o2xKI2stbibVxBMhsyxxgeRm9lAubwqSaGbm4X6kfPQ5Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D55\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">好了，祝大家在新的一年，无论个人还是组织，都能与 AI/ 智能体共同成长。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">甲方的投资都没打水漂，乙方的饼/瓜都能如愿变现</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
